author: bobharner
msg: Added meta tag to tell IE to render in IE 9 standards mode. This is a work-around for the autoexport plugin bug that prevents the DOCTYPE declaration from appearing at the top of the HTML, which makes IE render in Quirks mode. This work-around *should* fix all the page layout bugs seen in IE.
